OL,3,CWatchdog set to fine South East Water
OL,4,C#22m over water supply failures
OL,6,FOfwat has said it plans to fine South
OL,7,FEast Water #22 million over water
OL,8,Fsupply failures between 2020 and 2023
OL,9,Fimpacting more than 286,000 people.
OL,11,FThe water regulator said it was
OL,12,Fconsulting over the fine after homes
OL,13,Fin Kent and Sussex were hit by
OL,14,Fmultiple supply interruptions over the
OL,15,Fyears.
OL,17,FSouth East Water "lacked ownership"
OL,18,Ffor fixing the root cause of supply
OL,19,Ffailures and did not maintain
OL,20,Fimportant infrastructure, the watchdog
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,26,@yD@ROUyD@cO]
