PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772741478
OL,3,CWatchdog set to fine South East Water
OL,4,C#22m over water supply failures
OL,6,FIt said its investigations found that
OL,7,Fthe water company "failed to maintain
OL,8,Fsupply-system resilience" to minimise
OL,9,Fincidents occurring and failed to plan
OL,10,Fto make sure it had sufficient
OL,11,Fheadroom to deal with periods of high
OL,12,Fdemand.
OL,14,FIn the most recent incident more than
OL,15,F24,000 homes in Tunbridge Wells lost
OL,16,Ftheir water supply with schools and
OL,17,Fcare homes disrupted in the lead-up to
OL,18,FChristmas.
OL,26,@oD@SOUpD@YO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
