FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772741478
OL,3,CWatchdog set to fine South East Water
OL,4,C#22m over water supply failures
OL,6,FIt was estimated that businesses lost
OL,7,Fa combined total of somewhere between
OL,8,F#10 million and #20 million because of
OL,9,Fthe crisis.
OL,11,FLast month the boss of South East
OL,12,FWater, David Hinton revealed the
OL,13,Foutage which left tens of thousands of
OL,14,Fpeople in Kent with no running water,
OL,15,Fcost the company almost #30 million.
OL,17,FChris Walters, interim chief executive
OL,18,Fof Ofwat, said: "South East Water's
OL,19,Fsignificant failings caused major
OL,20,Fdisruption and had a huge impact on
OL,21,Fthousands of its customers.
OL,26,@zD@QOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
