OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772741478
OL,3,CWatchdog set to fine South East Water
OL,4,C#22m over water supply failures
OL,6,F"Not only did the company fail in its
OL,7,Fduty to provide a water supply to meet
OL,8,Fthe demands of its customers, but it
OL,9,Falso fell short when it came to
OL,10,Fproviding support for customers who
OL,11,Flost their supply.
OL,13,F"They must do better."
OL,15,FA spokesperson for South East Water
OL,16,Fsaid: "We recently filed for judicial
OL,17,Freview of an Ofwat draft decision and
OL,18,Fsought an injunction.
OL,20,F"Following a hearing, the court did
OL,21,Fnot grant the interim injunction.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUuD@VO]xD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
