PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772741478
OL,3,CWatchdog set to fine South East Water
OL,4,C#22m over water supply failures
OL,6,F"We respect the court's decision on
OL,7,Fthis.
OL,9,F"We are now considering Ofwat's draft
OL,10,Fdecision and will respond via the
OL,11,Fappropriate channels, ahead of its
OL,12,Ffinal decision. We have no further
OL,13,Fcomment at this time."
